/span><span class="token plain"> AccountNodeDIDClientConfig</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    options</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">?</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token builtin">any</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    countryCode</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">?</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token builtin">string</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">}</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><ul><li><code>privateKey</code> - Verida network private key for the account</li><li><code>environment</code> - Verida environment (<code>EnvironmentType.TESTNET</code> or <code>EnvironmentType.MAINNET</code>)</li><li><code>didClientConfig</code> - Instance of <code>AccountNodeDIDClientConfig</code></li><li><code>countryCode</code> - (optional) Country to use for selecting storage and DID nodes on the network. If not specified, will choose random global nodes. If specified, will use nodes in that country. If not enough nodes are available in that country, it will fallback to selecting nodes in the same region as that country, then fallback to global nodes.</li></ul></div></article><nav class="pagination-nav docusaurus-mt-lg" aria-label="Docs pages"><a class="pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--prev" href="/docs/client-sdk/how-it-works"><div class="pagination-nav__sublabel">Previous</div><div class="pagination-nav__label">How it Works</div></a><a class="pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--next" href="/docs/client-sdk/data"><div class="pagination-nav__sublabel">Next</div><div class="pagination-nav__label">Data</div></a></nav></div></div><div class="col col--3"><div class="tableOfContents_bqdL thin-scrollbar theme-doc-toc-desktop"><ul class="table-of-contents table-of-contents__left-border"><li><a href="#1-verida-wallet" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">1. Verida Wallet</a></li><li><a href="#2-private-key" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">2. Private Key</a><ul><li><a href="#example" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Example</a></li><li><a href="#web3config" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Web3Config</a></li><li><a href="#generate-private-key" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Generate private key</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#advanced" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Advanced</a><ul><li><a href="#accountnode-config" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">AccountNode Config</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div></div></main></div></div><footer class="footer"><div class="container container-fluid"><div class="row footer__links"><div class="col footer__col"><div class="footer__title">Product</div><ul class="footer__items clean-list"><li class="footer__item"><a